<p><strong>Registration &amp; Questionnaires</strong></p>
<p>Please <a href="https://wimr.snapforms.com.au/form/registration?new%20patient=[PATIENT]&amp;adult%20or%20paed=Adult&amp;research%20or%20clinic=Clinic&amp;consult%20or%20sleep=Consult&amp;first%20name=[FIRST_NAME]&amp;last%20name=[LAST_NAME]&amp;dob=[DOB]">click here</a> and complete your registration form before attending for your appointment. Please also take the time to complete our standard set of questionnaires <a href="https://wimr.snapforms.com.au/form/psychology-questionnaires?first%20name=[FIRST_NAME]&amp;last%20name=[LAST_NAME]&amp;dob=[DOB]">here</a>. It is <strong> extremely important </strong> to complete
these forms before your attendance to enable your consultation to commence on time.</p>
<p>The cost of your initial consultation will be $300. We accept EFTPOS, credit cards including AMEX without surcharge (no Diners Club), or cash. We can submit your claim to Medicare on site with a valid referral and Medicare details.</p>
<p>Please note that this is a private clinic and we do not Bulk Bill.</p>
<p><strong>Cancellation Fees</strong></p>
<p>When a patient cancels their appointment or does not attend without giving notice, they prevent another patient from being seen.&nbsp; Therefore, we require 2 business days notice for any appointment changes. A charge of $100 will apply for any appointment changes that may occur without appropriate notice.&nbsp;</p>
